gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 111, Rockets 90
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Rockets, 111-90. Anthony Edwards recorded 32 points (22 in the 3rd quarter) and 6 rebounds for the Timberwolves, with Rudy Gobert adding 17 points and 13 rebounds in the victory. Alperen Segun tallied 15 points and 10 rebounds for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 35-15, while the Rockets fall to 23-26.
